  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1_48",
    "text": "陈老爷子的三个“铁饭碗”",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.014040183974824498,
      0.780908860116781,
      0.3054950375211813,
      0.8093424727088093
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1",
    "order": 49
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1_58",
    "text": "服务“三农”是农行改革发展永恒主题",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.35294117647058826,
      0.7866632817127867,
      0.9828128782377148,
      0.8232207836168233
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1",
    "order": 50
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1_49",
    "text": "75岁的陈荣亮老人是贵州省贵 阳市白云区艳山红镇尖坡村的一位 农民，谈及这几年来的生活，老人说： “在寨子里活了大半辈子，却在短短 这几年时间，就得到了上面给的三个 “铁饭碗’。”",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.00823045267489712,
      0.8174663620208175,
      0.15298959089808764,
      0.8672251840568672
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1",
    "order": 51
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1_52",
    "text": "2009年前，他和老伴每人月领134.01 元，今年又“升值”了，一月领到了 148.48元。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1646090534979424,
      0.8178048574088178,
      0.307915758896151,
      0.8421765253448422
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1",
    "order": 52
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1_59",
    "text": "访中国农业银长张云",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.5199709513435004,
      0.8266057374968266,
      0.8138465262648269,
      0.8428535161208428
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1",
    "order": 53
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1_53",
    "text": "农村合作医疗开展后，陈荣亮和 老伴这几年看病都能报销一部分。 “如果生病住院花费上万元，也可以 报销60%以上。有了这个新农合，我 们这些老人感觉有保障了。”老人说。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1646090534979424,
      0.8435305068968435,
      0.3093681917211329,
      0.8844884488448845
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d6cd76e5afe881630173bd4921531a4b_1",
    "order": 54
  },
  {
